OL,3,CBoy, 15, and two adults arrested in NI
OL,4,Cpolice station car bomb probe
OL,6,FA teenage boy, a man and a woman have
OL,7,Fbeen arrested by police investigating
OL,8,Fan attempted car bomb attempt on
OL,9,FLurgan police station.
OL,11,FThe dissident republican group the New
OL,12,FIRA claimed responsibility for the
OL,13,Fincident in March that saw a food
OL,14,Fdelivery driver hijacked in Kilwilkie
OL,15,Fand forced to drive a "crude but
OL,16,Fviable" device to the station.
OL,18,FJustice Minister Naomi Long said it
OL,19,Fwould have caused devastation if it
OL,20,Fhad detonated.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@GO]
