OL,3,CBoy, 15, and two adults arrested in NI
OL,4,Cpolice station car bomb probe
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, police said they had
OL,7,Farrested a 48-year-old man and a 15-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy under the Terrorism Act.
OL,10,FBoth were taken to Musgrave Serious
OL,11,FCrime Suite for questioning.
OL,13,FA police spokesperson added that a 39-
OL,14,Fyear-old woman was subsequently
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of perverting
OL,16,Fthe course of justice, obstructing
OL,17,Fpolice and assisting an offender.
OL,19,FAll three were arrested in the Lurgan
OL,20,Farea, where a number of searches
OL,21,Fremain ongoing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
