OL,3,CBoy, 15, and two adults arrested in NI
OL,4,Cpolice station car bomb probe
OL,6,FA Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "This cowardly and
OL,8,Fwidely condemned attack, which took
OL,9,Fplace on the night of Monday March 30,
OL,10,Fput innocent lives at risk.
OL,12,F"I'm keen to offer assurance that we
OL,13,Fwill continue in our efforts to bring
OL,14,Fthose responsible to justice, and
OL,15,Fwould encourage anyone with
OL,16,Finformation to get in touch."
OL,18,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,19,Fcontact detectives on 101, quoting
OL,20,Freference 1828 of March 30.
